{"tid":196451,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[惠英紅x陳家樂] 羅耀輝《幸運是我》Happiness 周四起重新上映","createTime":"2017-04-11T10:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T16:18:29.000Z","uid":4260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfced8cb9b4e42d12ffe085da038e1cdda7d9ba","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"Happiness 幸運是我<br />\n2 hrs &middot;<br />\n<br />\n恭喜惠英紅憑《幸運是我》榮獲第36届香港電影金像獎最佳女主角!<br />\n《幸運是我》載譽歸來<br />\n本週四 (4月13日) 於以下院線再度上映:<br />\nUA Cine Times<br />\nUA Cine Moko<br />\n#惠英紅<br />\n#最佳女主角<br />\n#陳家樂<br />\n#羅耀輝<br />\n#幸運是我<br />\n#英皇電影<br />\n#香港電影金像獎<br />\n#第36屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/movie/MovieDetail?key=4144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uacinemas.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fmovie%2FMovieDetail%3Fkey%3D4144&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ed342f3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/movie/MovieDetail?key=4144</a>"},{"pid":"54e7c57b49ee7c388cdd8b3c823bb45083b6796c","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-0/p480x480/17835200_1365936646829567_5643482441159950327_o.jpg?oh=bd00a441dbc7e728c5456eda767600ef&amp;oe=595B22A3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-0%2Fp480x480%2F17835200_1365936646829567_5643482441159950327_o.jpg%3Foh%3Dbd00a441dbc7e728c5456eda767600ef%26oe%3D595B22A3&h=dc5c1c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電影《幸運是我》終極預告‧9月8日相知相守 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=URQEPcOZ7pA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DURQEPcOZ7pA&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7936c197\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=URQEPcOZ7pA</a><br />\n<br />\n電影主題曲 林欣彤 Mag Lam《幸運是我》[Official MV] <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jEA1lRuSwM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1jEA1lRuSwM&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=bd6811e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jEA1lRuSwM</a><br />\n<br />\n惠英紅勇奪今屆最佳女主角得獎感受<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8trTl_e8B4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8trTl_e8B4A&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4104b4de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8trTl_e8B4A</a>"},{"pid":"e2cd6c7eb6e48532a449ccb6e2737a10e17e3d58","tid":196451,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"電影節唔播呢套唯有自己睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小紅姐演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6b98a3b60425ed3faddf1adb98ee585e356408","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:21:42.000Z","msg":"羅耀輝《幸運是我》周四起重映<br />\n<br />\n第三十六屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮已於周日晚完滿結束，而各獎項亦名花有主，當中惠英紅憑著英皇發行、羅耀輝執導、陳家樂合演的《幸運是我》奪得最佳女主角的獎項。英皇發行方面、也隨著安排這部得獎電影於周四起重映。<br />\n<br />\n《幸運是我》於去年九月八日在香港上映，最終上映六星期錄得近250萬的票房成績，而當時觀眾的反映不俗，除了對於女主角惠英紅的演出予以肯定外，同時亦讚賞陳家樂在演出上有所突破。是次重映安排在本周四開畫，分別於銅鑼灣UA Cine Times上映下午五時廿五分及晚上七時四十五分的場次，以及於旺角UA Cine Moko上映下午四時三十五分次，戲票已可於上映戲院票房及網上購買。<br />\n<br />\n倘若去年未能到戲院觀賞《幸運是我》的觀眾，也許可以把握機會，於大銀幕觀賞惠英紅的精彩演出好了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F55194&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=234454b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55194</a>"},{"pid":"404893a29f15b4a66e2efe720ff747319e1fa098","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電影節唔播呢套唯有自己睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小紅姐演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11f1850f185cc89092f0e4fee9873b425e54dbb","tid":196451,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"濕鳩UA要成舊水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e04a71eada0969c181c79ce028d84eeca3f7ad1","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕鳩UA要成舊水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有學生飛都勁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b71a5fa60e106ebe3521c51c69fcba89c096e33","tid":196451,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1c9f161ea0e6f25750b6d974de74933035b9ae","tid":196451,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"之前已經入場睇左2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786989af3d81183fa265e26629665c7c41224bf","tid":196451,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:36:04.000Z","msg":"之前行碟舖已經見到出咗碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0b36e399fa71b200629311756bc3ddecd3476","tid":196451,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e347612964e52280da9e4e0df1d6f37d203905fb","tid":196451,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockq